00:00:04.615 --> 00:00:06.990
So, that's going to be getting the motors ready to take

00:00:06.990 --> 00:00:09.518
commands and releasing the motors from that state.

00:00:09.518 --> 00:00:14.070
So, down into the right is going to arm the motors which gets them to start spinning.

00:00:14.070 --> 00:00:16.350
And when you want to kind of turn everything off,

00:00:16.350 --> 00:00:17.810
it's going be down and to the left.

00:00:17.809 --> 00:00:21.644
And down to the right again to arm.

00:00:21.644 --> 00:00:26.300
And I have throttle up and make the vehicle take off.

00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:29.574
I can yaw and fly at high speed into the wall to the right,

00:00:29.574 --> 00:00:34.399
fly at high speed into the wall to the left.

