We're actually able to change the configurations on the autopilot and one of them

00:00:55.789 --> 00:00:59.744
is to configure the switches to be able to change different control modes.

00:00:59.744 --> 00:01:01.699
So one of the things you're going to want to do is go through

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:05.344
that configuration process before you take your vehicle outside.

00:01:05.344 --> 00:01:07.939
Very much so. So, we've got two sets of

00:01:07.939 --> 00:01:09.439
switches are going to help us get

00:01:09.439 --> 00:01:11.719
through all the different states that we're going to want.

00:01:11.719 --> 00:01:13.609
When this switch is all the way towards you,

00:01:13.609 --> 00:01:15.450
when both this switches are all the way towards you.

00:01:15.450 --> 00:01:16.730
This one and this one.

00:01:16.730 --> 00:01:18.530
Correct.

00:01:18.530 --> 00:01:20.625
That's going to be manual control.

00:01:20.625 --> 00:01:24.484
So, that's going to be the most basic amount of input that you can get.

00:01:24.484 --> 00:01:28.176
This top switch in middle position,

00:01:28.176 --> 00:01:31.424
is what we are going to call our main assisted modes.

00:01:31.424 --> 00:01:34.534
So, middle position bottom that's going to be altitude mode.

00:01:34.534 --> 00:01:36.009
So, the vehicle is going to try and hold

00:01:36.010 --> 00:01:39.140
its altitude which means you don't have to worry as much about the throttling input.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:40.820
But it will drift left and right. Correct.

00:01:40.819 --> 00:01:45.284
Middle position is position control.

00:01:45.284 --> 00:01:48.500
And that means it's going to be working to hold its position.

00:01:48.500 --> 00:01:51.137
So, when you release your hand from all the commands,

00:01:51.137 --> 00:01:54.055
it should hold where it is and not drift with any wind.

00:01:54.055 --> 00:01:57.208
And then finally, when it's time to turn that script on

00:01:57.207 --> 00:01:59.900
all the way up, puts it into off-board control.

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:04.145
